textAnnotations.description:
AS ALOYAL
REPUBLICAN
I WAS ALL SET TO
VOTE FOR
MITTROMNEY
BUT THEN
NEWT GINGRICH AND
RICK PERRY
CONVINCED MEE
HE'S A
VULTURE CAPITALIST
WHO DOESN' T CARE
ABOUT THE
MIDDLE CLASS
SONOW I'M
HEEDING THEIR
WARNING AND
SWITCHING MY
SUPPORT...
TO
BARACK
OBAMA
